
##  Quick Start (Run the Project)

Follow these steps to set up and run the PAN Card Detection system:

### 1️  Clone the Repository
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/pan-card-detection-yolov8.git
cd pan-card-detection-yolov8


### 2️  Set Up Environment

  python -m venv venv

### 3️ Install Requirements

  pip install -r requirements.txt

### 4 Train the Model

  python train.py

### 5 Run Detection
  python detect.py
